</sense>
<sense n=""2""><number>2</number><trans> employ a trick to catch s.o. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Dì siya madiritsu ug dakup. Laángun giyud,</i><trans> He can’t be caught easily. He should be trapped. </trans></eg>
