<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Lab-as nga búlak,</i><trans> Fresh flowers. </trans></eg>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Lab-as isdà,</i><trans> <tr>Fresh fish</tr>. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""2""><number>2</number><trans> fresh in manner. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Lab-as ra kaáyu nang ímung panlihuklihuk,</i><trans> Your actions are very fresh. </trans></eg>
