<sense n=""1""><number>1</number> <itype>[B; c1]</itype><trans> <tr>sink deeply</tr>. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Milábu ang ayis pik sa dughan ni Kindi,</i><trans> The ice pick sank deep into Candy’s breast. </trans></eg>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Mu ra ka man ug bairan nga nalábu sa lápuk,</i><trans> You take forever to come back when I send you s.w. (Lit. You are like a whetstone thrown into the mud and fail to come up.) </trans></eg>
