</sense>
<sense n=""2""><number>2</number><trans> act spoiled and abusive from having been pampered. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Naglangì nà siya kay labánan man.</i><trans> He has gotten uncontrollable because s.o. always takes his side. </trans></eg>
</sense></hom>
<hom role=""a""><pos>a</pos>
<sense n=""0""><trans> asking for affection, being spoiled. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Kanang íyang pagpangáyug pagkáun ági lang nag langì,</i><trans> When she asks for food like that she’s just asking for attention.
