<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Mulánug (malánug) ang ímung tíngug ug magmigapun ka,</i><trans> Your voice will become loud if you use a megaphone. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""2""><number>2</number> <itype>[A]</itype><trans> echo, resound. </trans>
