<sense n=""2a""><number>2a</number><trans> echoes, reminiscenses of the past. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Kining mga awíta mga lánug lámang sa kanhíay,</i><trans> These songs are but echoes of the past. </trans></eg>
</sense></hom>
