<sense n=""3""><number>3</number> <itype>[B16; c1]</itype><trans> be, become straight. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Naglargu lang ning sinináa mu rag sáku,</i><trans> This dress is straight at the sides like a sack. </trans></eg>
